>>Fairness under composition states that by satisfying group or individual fairness in isolation, whole systems built by these isolated classifiers are fair.|| Is this statement true or false? <<

( ) True {{Classifiers that are fair in isolation (individual or group fairness) do not necessarily compose into fair systems.}}
